}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "ZyXEL", "45-401-000619", and "Made in China" is silkscreened on the board :in the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=717819 FCC photos].
There is an additional model sharing this name with FCC ID I88P660HWDXV2.. :ZyXEL P-660HW-D1 (Annex A)/D3 (Annex B)/D7 (VER2) [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=717823 FCC schematics]
An additional (unprivlidged) account appears to be accessible with password '''user'''. :Default settings are per the FCC manual.
